{"title" : "军营一日一夜体验拓展（内含：短时军训、军营内务体验、家庭军营拓展、家庭徒步障碍穿越、）" ,"content":"<P class=pa-8 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>军营一日一夜体验拓展是将军营生活体验与户外拓展活动相结合。家庭成员需要克服日常懒散的生活习惯、融入部队集体军事化的生活当中来。对于有孩子的家庭，通过各项拓展活动的集体配合，培养孩子们的自立与团队荣誉感，同时军营生活可培养孩子们良好的日常生活习惯。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;套餐内拓展项目简介：</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1><BR></SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>短时军训：早操军训时间设置为30-60分钟，为短时军训。以完成团队分配、破冰、团队口号及队长等准备为首要任务。其次进行队列制式动作的训练。目的是端正姿态，保持严整的团队阵容，养成令行禁止和严格遵守纪律的习惯，培养迅速、准确、协调一致的作风。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>军营生活体验：家庭成员提前一晚到达军营，在军营一日拓展期间，生活与内务完全采用部队</SPAN></P><P class=pa-5 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>军事化管理，从晨间出操、餐饮、作息、生活用品整理、均与部队战士相同管理办</SPAN></P><P class=pa-5 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>法。真正体验军营整齐、统一、服从的纪律风范。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>拓展训练：金牌上百种拓展活动，根据家庭教育特点进行筛选。常言说：“身教胜于言传”，在活动中，让家庭成员通过切身的体会，感受到来自于团队的力量，并对自身力量与极限有更直观的认识。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>徒步穿越：在绿树成荫的大山内，设置短途徒步穿越，穿越途中设置一定的障碍与游戏，如挖宝、任务完成等，对于达成目标的家庭，设有相应奖品。</SPAN></P><P class=pa-2 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1><BR></SPAN></P><P class=pa-14 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>报名参加办法：</SPAN></P><P class=pa-1 style='WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT: medium 'Times New Roman'; LETTER-SPACING: normal; TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px'><SPAN class=ca-1>提前一周报名，满6组家庭成班，详情电话咨询。</SPAN></P>"}